documentation.text:
We include "role" and "completedBy" in both events to see them
 right in Ganache's logs when a task is created or toggled.

Toggles the task's completed status and records who completed it.
 If the task is being reverted to incomplete, set "completedBy" to an empty string.

TaskCreated(uint256,string,bool,uint256,.notice: We include "role" and "completedBy" in both events to see them right in Ganache's logs when a task is created or toggled.

toggleCompleted(uint256,string).notice: Toggles the task's completed status and records who completed it. If the task is being reverted to incomplete, set "completedBy" to an empty string.
